{"tid":1483281,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"正式宣佈 今晚邊個阻街塞路唔返屋企嘅都係警察臥底！","createTime":"2019-08-18T11:16:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T14:30:34.000Z","uid":195944,"like":349,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":65,"replies":[{"pid":"cdecfc240be72e05aa057e2dbfba659a21f2ff47","tid":1483281,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T11:16:40.000Z","msg":"去完維園<br />\n返咗屋企 <br />\n打開電視<br />\n見到班警厹著晒gear 俾雨淋濕晒個樣就好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n正式宣佈 今晚有鬼搞事嘅話<br />\n全部都係警厹嘅臥底黎<br />\n係政府一手一腳搞出黎嘅大龍鳳<br />\n<br />\n同二百萬香港市民無關<br />\n你班警厹唔駛指意賴落我地度<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"465587afe41f69d7e4edd8efaaf95c6ca510b2fe","tid":1483281,"uid":125757,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T11:19:22.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"bf918cca44990ea7a7a2179ac3ee31c5e6c67406","tid":1483281,"uid":290883,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T11:19:32.000Z","msg":"返屋企訓覺！！"},{"pid":"7ca901d4851bbd5ab76cc29c9091b73a84467d07","tid":1483281,"uid":149904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T11:20:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ced97c8e0182bc3377b314f2f2c64c60a3145ce1","tid":1483281,"uid":195944,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T11:26:32.000Z","msg":"想我地落搭？ <br />\n返屋企瞓喇支那警厹<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08cc6955dc126ed22556721451c68db853afaa7c","tid":1483281,"uid":305449,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T11:27:31.000Z","msg":"集完會有咩做？<br />\n1. 攰了，肚餓了，番屋企休息下<br />\n2. 仲有氣有力，搭返炮台山，去多次維園<br />\n小弟不才選了1, 對唔住咁多位巴絲<br />\n<br />\n其他？今日不了<br />\n300萬人和平集會係世界上幾乎前無古人，唔好意氣用事比人挑撥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nP.s. 如果用尋日賣港派每平方米企40人既系數黎計，818應該可以破千萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />